Speed Factor: 7
Proficiency Type: Two-handed Sword
Type: Two-handed
Requires:
 14 Strength

Weight: 9~

@6680 = ~Forged in the black heart of the Abyss by tanar'ri sorcerers for use in the eternal Blood War, this blade was once wielded by the infamous babau assassin Khazzrax the Gasping Death. Lore tells of a blade, black as the night, that Khazzrax would use to slash his victims open, causing fire to briefly flare out of the fresh wound.

In addition to the sword's regular properties, the demon Azothet has been bound within its blade. As she rages with demonic fury at her captivity, the sword is thus empowered.

