@6690 = ~Forged in the black heart of the Abyss by tanar'ri sorcerers for use in the eternal Blood War, this blade was once wielded by the infamous babau assassin Khazzrax the Gasping Death. Lore tells of a blade, black as the night, that Khazzrax would use to slash his victims open, causing fire to briefly flare out of the fresh wound.

In addition to the sword's regular properties, two rival demons have been magically bound within its blade. As they rage with fury at each other and at their shared captivity, they thus empower the blade.

