@70030 = ~Create Bruiser Mates
This ability crafts 10 of Jan's patented Flasher Master Bruiser Mates, adding them to the user's inventory. Handle with care!~


@70040 = ~This is a well-crafted locket, obviously made with care, and typical of keepsake items often given to loved ones. A minor enchantment has attempted to capture the likeness of both <CHARNAME> and Jaheira within, making it a thoughtful gift of remembrance. One side has suffered some smudging, but it is a sweet gift nonetheless.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
– Hit Points: +5

Weight: 1~

@70041 = ~Only Jaheira or <CHARNAME> may use this locket.~
